exif:ImageDescription: It is thought the man on the left to be Tom O'Folliard, one of The Regulators and Billy's best friend. On the right is a woman Guijarro believes to be Sallie Chisum, niece of the prominent cattle rancher John Chisum. Charged with protecting Chisum...s cows from the Murphy-Dolan gangs, Billy and his cohorts made periodical visits to the Chisum ranch. Sallie had no shortage of suitors, and Billy stood out among her admirers. Photo: Courtesy of Randy Guijarro.
